{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)resume","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"resume"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a pack resumes after being suspended, it may begin by iterating over the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already downloaded resources. As a result, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" structure’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"countOfResourcesCompleted"},{"type":"text","text":" field may revert to 0 before rapidly returning to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the level of progress at the time the pack was suspended."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To temporarily suspend downloading, call the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-suspend"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/resume":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"resume"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"resume"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume","title":"resume","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","title":"MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]}}}